<section class="member-post--summary"><p>In preparation of the upcoming Spring Boot 1.4.4 release, I am pleased to announce the availability of the seventh service release of Spring Data release train Hopper. The release ships <a href="https://jira.spring.io/issues/?filter=15466">39 tickets fixed</a> and is a recommended upgrade for all users.</p>
