<li>Spring Data for Apache Cassandra 1.4.7 - <a href="https://repo.spring.io/libs-release/org/springframework/data/spring-data-cassandra/1.4.7.RELEASE">Artifacts</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/cassandra/docs/1.4.7.RELEASE/api">JavaDocs</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/cassandra/docs/1.4.7.RELEASE/reference/html">Documentation</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/cassandra/docs/1.4.7.RELEASE/changelog.txt">Changelog</a></li>
